      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use. It has been maintained enough to keep it running smoothly, though it is not a showpiece. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility and function over a perfect appearance.",
