      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious care. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, confirms its status as a premier example of its class. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its original delivery state in every significant detail. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this peerless offering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
